COMMITTEE AMENDMENT

COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to S.P. 251, L.D. 753
1 SUMMARY
22 This amendment replaces the bill and changes the title. The amendment authorizes the
33 use of securities issued for the purpose of planning, purchasing, financing, acquiring,
44 constructing, renovating, furnishing, equipping, improving, extending, enlarging and
55 consolidating new and existing facilities and projects relating to the judicial branch to
66 include such facilities in Penobscot County.
77 FISCAL NOTE REQUIRED
88 (See attached)
